---
const lang = Astro.props.lang;
---
<section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-brand-blueFinca sm:text-4xl mb-4 text-center">
        {lang === "es" 
          ? "Lo que dicen nuestros clientes" 
          : lang === "en" 
          ? "What our clients say" 
          : "Was unsere kunden sagen"}
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review">
            <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating">
                <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" />
                <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-2">
                    <span>★★★★★</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody" class="italic">
                {lang === "es" 
                  ? "Excelente servicio de administración para mi apartamento en Tenerife Sur. Se encargan de todo y han maximizado los ingresos de mi vivienda vacacional." 
                  : lang === "en" 
                  ? "Excellent management service for my apartment in South Tenerife. They take care of everything and have maximized my vacation rental income." 
                  : "Ausgezeichneter Verwaltungsservice für meine Wohnung im Süden Teneriffas. Sie kümmern sich um alles und haben meine Einnahmen aus der Ferienvermietung maximiert."}
            </blockquote>
            <div class="mt-4 font-medium" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
                <span itemprop="name">
                    {lang === "es" ? "Carlos M." : lang === "en" ? "Richard T." : "Michael S."}
                </span>
                <meta itemprop="nationality" content={lang === "es" ? "ES" : lang === "en" ? "UK" : "DE"} />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review">
            <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating">
                <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" />
                <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-2">
                    <span>★★★★★</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody" class="italic">
                {lang === "es" 
                  ? "Como propietario extranjero, contar con un administrador de confianza en Tenerife es fundamental. Su equipo es profesional y siempre responde rápidamente." 
                  : lang === "en" 
                  ? "As a foreign owner, having a trustworthy property manager in Tenerife is essential. Their team is professional and always responds quickly." 
                  : "Als ausländischer Eigentümer ist es wichtig, einen vertrauenswürdigen Immobilienverwalter auf Teneriffa zu haben. Ihr Team ist professionell und reagiert immer schnell."}
            </blockquote>
            <div class="mt-4 font-medium" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
                <span itemprop="name">
                    {lang === "es" ? "Ana P." : lang === "en" ? "Sarah L." : "Brigitte K."}
                </span>
                <meta itemprop="nationality" content={lang === "es" ? "ES" : lang === "en" ? "UK" : "DE"} />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>